org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM projects WHERE (projects.status = 1 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (7, 12)) OR projects.id = 1) AND projects.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT project_id FROM projects_trackers) AND projects.id = "$1" LIMIT 1
